<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">HOW TO EXPLAIN BITCOIN TO YOUR MOM <span class="divider">Â |Â </span></span><!-- end .title --> Have questions about how virtual currencies work? The comic artist Rami Niemi and Rachel Abrams of DealBook <b><a href="//www.nytimes.com/interactive/2014/04/02/business/dealbook/How-to-explain-bitcoin-to-your-mom.html">have all the answers</a></b>.</p>
